Class MoneyMarket

java.lang.Object
banking.project3.Account
banking.project3.Savings
banking.project3.MoneyMarket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
public class MoneyMarket extends Savings
Represents a Money Market account, which is a type of Savings account. This class extends the Savings class and provides additional functionality specific to Money Market accounts.
Author:
Zain Zulfiqar, Nicholas Yim
